libsodium

Sources:  https://github.com/jedisct1/libsodium
Releases: https://download.libsodium.org/libsodium/releases
Docs:     http://doc.libsodium.org/

# Prepare

Use release tarball named libsodium_%ver%.tar.gz

Repack original tarball as
libsodium-%ver%/libsodium_%ver%.orig.tar.bz2

# Usage

Arch - use libsodium package from community repo.
